        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Boston</placeName>
                <date>Feby 3d 5623</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Yours duly recd and in reply I bet to state<lb/> that when I wrote
                you the last time I had several<lb/> applications for the books I ordered, but not
                receiving<lb/> your answer neither your books, I concluded that<lb/> you declined to
                send any, and in reality I cannot<lb/> blame you as you lost a large amt of
                money.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">A Christian applied for Daily Prayer books,<lb/> so also a
                    <persName>Mr Pierce</persName> &amp; <persName>Hayner</persName>, but whither
                they<lb/> would take them now I cannot say. I could<lb/> have sold a Set of
                    <add>?</add> to a man at <placeName>Ly<add>?</add></placeName><lb/> but I could
                not comply with his request</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">You can do as you like send or not<lb/> I am not sure whether I can
                dispose of them<lb/> now. Our C<add>?</add> has finally purchased the
                Ch<add>?</add><lb/> and in <date>July</date>
                <add>?</add>; will be consecrated. As regards<lb/> of <add>מזרח</add> there is no
                other alternative as to build<lb/> the <add>היכל</add> on the <placeName>South
                    West</placeName> side and I myself see<lb/> no difficulty in doing so when I
                refer to the real<lb/>
                <add>?</add> &amp; where it <sic>amanates</sic> from and <sic>infference</sic> to
                be<lb/> drawn from certain <add>דינים</add>, it is entirely prohibited<lb/> to
                listen to the voice of the Reformers it is true and<lb/> we have to be careful, but
                in this matter I am not<lb/>
                <sic>affraid</sic>. Please look to various <add>דינים</add> &amp; you will
                consider<lb/> with me    </p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">Respy yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">Simon C Voot</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
